title: 100-Proof
detail: In need of inspiration? Press a button to make a cocktail of your choice. No fuss and no cleaning!
extended_details:
The 3D Cocktail Printer makes you a cocktail of your choice simply by pressing a button! 

* Choose from an updated and refreshing list of drink options!
* Make your own drinks! The Printer is programmable for the hobbyist bartender in you!
* No fuss, no cleaning! All you need is a glass!


The Printer also comes with facial recognition features to ensure safe and responsible drinking!

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vDSxkru7BCNRnNGhuiKurxnfFoGU5Pj5rFOhP0uoYEc/edit
